WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:08.559
CTA offers several ways to plan your trip,
whether it be the conventional map or online

00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:09.570
trip planners.

00:00:09.570 --> 00:00:13.330
We aim to provide you with a variety of options
to find your way.

00:00:13.330 --> 00:00:18.550
One of the easiest ways to plan a trip is
to use a trip planning service which can give

00:00:18.550 --> 00:00:23.840
you step-by-step directions suited to a specific
trip you plan to take.

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:29.439
Google Maps, Go Room, or the RTA travel information
center can all help you plan your trip.

00:00:29.439 --> 00:00:35.290
Visit transitchicago.com to plan trips online.

00:00:35.290 --> 00:00:40.380
With Google Transit, you can get transit and
walking directions from Google Maps which

00:00:40.380 --> 00:00:44.780
you can do conveniently in the planet trip
widget on transitchicago.

00:00:44.780 --> 00:00:45.910
com.

00:00:45.910 --> 00:00:51.250
Trip plans include a variety of transit providers
including Metra, Amtrak and certain private

00:00:51.250 --> 00:00:53.230
bus services.

00:00:53.230 --> 00:00:58.730
You can also plan a trip online with Goroo
there are teas new multi-mobile trip planner.

00:00:58.730 --> 00:01:03.780
Goroo helps you get specific trip plans and
find scheduled service information, fares

00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:09.270
and other pertinent information for the CTA,
Metra, Pace and more.

00:01:09.270 --> 00:01:14.740
Goroo also allows you to specify if you need
a trip entirely using accessible services

00:01:14.740 --> 00:01:17.340
as an added feature.

00:01:17.340 --> 00:01:24.929
You can also get travel information from the
RTA travel information center by calling 312-836-7000.

00:01:24.929 --> 00:01:29.530
The center is open from 4:45 a.m. to 1:00
a.m. every day.

00:01:29.530 --> 00:01:34.270
For faster service have your start and end
points and the day and time you wish to travel.

00:01:34.270 --> 00:01:39.670
For travel information via TTY call 312-836-4949.

00:01:39.670 --> 00:01:46.240
And finally trip planning is also easy to
use when you're on the move.

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:51.139
The maps app on many smartphones also make
it easy to plan your trip when you're already

00:01:51.139 --> 00:01:53.060
in transit.

00:01:53.060 --> 00:01:59.780
Remember for all your transit needs go to
transitchicago.com or call the RTA travel

00:01:59.780 --> 00:02:04.920
information center at 312-836-7000.

